metadata.name: Digital Ikebana No°1
metadata.description:
Digital Ikebana is a collaboration between 3D artist Danny Essom and tattoo artist Html_mag. With each artist taking the lead on half of the compositions, in which they explore and replicate Modern Ikebana in their own style and medium. 

Resulting in a collection of 6 pieces available both as digital collectibles and tattoo flash. Making the series available to be collected on the blockchain, immortalising each composition like their flash counterpart.

-----------

Danny Essom (NaturallyAcidic) is a 3D artist from London exploring the future of nature through a surreal and manufactured lens.
